page.title: 20LOCAL HISTORY
page.content: The villages in this area were probaly established before the origanal Domesday book because many towns cities and villages have names which end in ing; ham; or ton,like Felmingham, Tuttington, Banningham. This means that they probaly started up in Saxon settlements. We at Colby C.P. school have enjoyed taking part in the 1985 Domesday Project.
